{"tid":1539562,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咪撚再問收唔收貨","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:56.000Z","uid":54392,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"980c49acccf60f2ce2930ecc8158611852a5695e","tid":1539562,"uid":54392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:07:47.000Z","msg":"咁多開post 問收唔收貨<br />\n我想講，係唔可能收貨！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家流左咁多血淚同人命先換黎撤回兩隻字<br />\n收貨嘅話對唔對得住佢地？<br />\n邊個再叫人收貨，邊個就係鬼，係分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c5c04e303f7c18caab8bc865b10cc328091ce50","tid":1539562,"uid":158718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:09:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Yw7R37Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYw7R37Z.jpg&h=56753a99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提提你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />記得9.7係全民㩒錢日！"},{"pid":"ebe6043a0b9b5a6baf559a5722da8f30da442a18","tid":1539562,"uid":22760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:49.000Z","msg":"邊撚個再講收貨，我屌撚死佢"},{"pid":"f41b085c00cc938ad3c3406d2ece7e5b9f96937b","tid":1539562,"uid":54392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:10:53.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49021cf376b00084decc60fd69bc034982b77a44","tid":1539562,"uid":94819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:11:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a3851c6f5ff3de11de2b6cdd5087ebe4d02838ae","tid":1539562,"uid":52727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:11:18.000Z","msg":"【教學】將Facebook/Youtube 影片文宣轉換成Twitter 文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1537277\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1537277</a><br />\n<br />\n1. 註冊Twitter 帳號。<br />\n2. 找到要post 上Twitter 的影片。<br />\n3. 複制facebook影片連結貼上到以下網頁 (需要登入及縛定Twitter 帳戶， facebook影片分享必需是公開)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://transferring-videos.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftransferring-videos.com&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcairXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=f7937618\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://transferring-videos.com</a><br />\n<br />\n4. 等待轉換時輸入英文標題，及加上 #chinazi 等 hash tag。<br />\n5. 選擇發佈至 Twitter。<br />\n<br />\n6. 【重要】我諗大家嘅Twitter應該都冇乜人follow, 記得copy自己Twitter post 嘅link, 然後以回覆方式貼上到名人的Twitter post 上！咁人地碌碌下當奴侵嘅twitter 就會見到黑警打示威者嘅片 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我做咗幾日已經多咗好多外國人睇，甚至開始有支那打手過黎留言。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93db74bb114a0fe1e56b714fbe37e7bb004771d","tid":1539562,"uid":258210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:11:30.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\nbin個袋住先我就同bin個割<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b08c8b64b7889a3e04cc7e9534b82d58ed2507","tid":1539562,"uid":314531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:12:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">啱！<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好畀柒婆混淆視聽，要對得住千幾個手足！<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1916864f34c6afb7abf0281cf378c0bc290cba79","tid":1539562,"uid":2662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:12:52.000Z","msg":"我哋要繼續推行動post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9c92f2125dbe48ee75b04fc5d2ae218c81c2f14","tid":1539562,"uid":266236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:15:56.000Z","msg":"唔洗問喇 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔收貨</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/p